text: Rudolf Karl González Vass (born 2 July 1998) is a German/Dominican professional footballer who plays as a winger for ZFC Meuselwitz and the Dominican Republic national team. ==International career== González was born in Germany to a Dominican father and a German mother. He is a youth international for Germany. He made his professional debut for the Dominican Republic national football team in a 1-0 friendly over win Guadeloupe on 15 February 2019. ===International goals=== :Scores and results list the Dominican Republic's goal tally first. {| class="wikitable" !
